title: Mowinckel
text:
Mowinckel is a Norwegian surname. Since the family was mainly involved with trade, many family members moved to trading centers in other countries to oversee the family interest there, and descendants can be found in the <a href="United%20States">United States</a>, <a href="Denmark">Denmark</a>, <a href="Venice">Venice</a> and quite a few others.
